                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        <p>
                            Sustaining communities is at the heart of Armenia Tree Project’s signature
                            tree planting program. Whether greening a public site or improving the quality of
                            life for an entire village, ATP’s carefully designed approach interconnects the education,
                            awareness, and economic empowerment that is vital to environmental sustainability and healthy living.
                            <br> <br>
                            Armenia Tree Project systematically revitalizes communities within
                            three years, taking into consideration all aspects of the land and its people.
                        </p>
                        <button class="sponsor-backyard-nursery-btn">Sponsor a Backyard Nursery</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-xs-12">
                        <div class="support-families">
                            <div class="title-and-play-button-wrapper">
                                <h3>How Armenian Villagers Are Using Trees <br />To Support Their Families</h3>
                                <a  data-toggle="modal" data-target="#how_planting_works"><img class="play-button" src="./img/play_btn.svg" alt=""></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="modal fade" id="how_planting_works" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="how_planting_works"
