                        <p><em>"BYN rewards family farmers for good work, when we pay for trees that have been well cared for,"
                                explains ATP Operations Manager Arthur Harutyunyan. "The program received an Energy Globe Award at the
                                European Parliament because of this program's
                                positive impact on the three aspects of sustainability: <span>people, profit & planet.</span>”</em></p>
